Всички текущи таблици
GRANT USAGE ON SCHEMA public TO iotuser;

GRANT SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE
ON ALL TABLES IN SCHEMA public
TO iotuser;

GRANT USAGE, SELECT, UPDATE
ON ALL SEQUENCES IN SCHEMA public
TO iotuser;

GRANT EXECUTE
ON ALL FUNCTIONS IN SCHEMA public
TO iotuser;
Всички бъдещи таблици

Това гарантира, че новосъздадените обекти също ще получават права:

ALTER DEFAULT PRIVILEGES FOR ROLE postgres IN SCHEMA public
GRANT SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE
ON TABLES TO iotuser;

ALTER DEFAULT PRIVILEGES FOR ROLE postgres IN SCHEMA public
GRANT USAGE, SELECT, UPDATE
ON SEQUENCES TO iotuser;

ALTER DEFAULT PRIVILEGES FOR ROLE postgres IN SCHEMA public
GRANT EXECUTE
ON FUNCTIONS TO iotuser;
Ако искаш iotuser да има абсолютно всички права (dev среда)
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES
ON ALL TABLES IN SCHEMA public
TO iotuser;

GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES
ON ALL SEQUENCES IN SCHEMA public
TO iotuser;

GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES
ON ALL FUNCTIONS IN SCHEMA public
TO iotuser;

ALTER DEFAULT PRIVILEGES FOR ROLE postgres IN SCHEMA public
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON TABLES TO iotuser;

ALTER DEFAULT PRIVILEGES FOR ROLE postgres IN SCHEMA public
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON SEQUENCES TO iotuser;

ALTER DEFAULT PRIVILEGES FOR ROLE postgres IN SCHEMA public
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON FUNCTIONS TO iotuser;
